    // =========================================================================
    // CRT Screen Simulation - Derived from cool-retro-term by Swordfish90
    // Original: https://github.com/Swordfish90/cool-retro-term
    // License: GPL-3.0
    //
    // Ported to Unity/Poiyomi by Foxipso
